1
00:00:05,920 --> 00:00:08,648
♫  I want to go to the future  ♫

2
00:00:08,648 --> 00:00:12,103
♫  Time bears witness to my quirkiness  ♫

3
00:00:12,103 --> 00:00:18,296
♫  I want to seize the day and put the whole world into my head  ♫

4
00:00:18,296 --> 00:00:21,022
♫  I want to go back in time to do all the crazy things I didn't do  ♫

5
00:00:21,022 --> 00:00:24,522
♫  I want to go back in time to do all the crazy things I didn't do  ♫

6
00:00:24,522 --> 00:00:31,043
♫  Don't say goodbye, don't be in a daze, let my radiant light be bright  ♫

7
00:00:31,043 --> 00:00:36,029
♫  We are always looking forward to the unknown future  ♫

8
00:00:36,029 --> 00:00:43,329
♫  And often overlooking our surroundings and best plan in front of us  ♫

9
00:00:43,329 --> 00:00:48,453
♫  Every day my heart beats for you  ♫

10
00:00:48,453 --> 00:00:49,866
♫  Be your light  ♫

11
00:00:49,866 --> 00:00:55,729
♫  You are no doubt irreplaceable  ♫

12
00:00:55,729 --> 00:01:02,229
♫  Every day the sun shines through the window  ♫

13
00:01:02,229 --> 00:01:08,396
♫  With your reflection being my incredible highlight  ♫

14
00:01:08,396 --> 00:01:11,844
[I Don't Want to be Brothers with You]

15
00:01:12,460 --> 00:01:15,240
It's just a TV interview.

16
00:01:15,240 --> 00:01:16,840
What's the big deal?

17
00:01:16,840 --> 00:01:19,499
Jin Libin, what are you doing?

18
00:01:20,530 --> 00:01:23,019
I'm eating kabobs. What does it look like?

19
00:01:23,019 --> 00:01:27,940
Did you eat pickled vegetables for lunch? Why are you mocking me with such sarcasm?

20
00:01:29,430 --> 00:01:32,079
So what if I'm mocking you?

21
00:01:35,760 --> 00:01:38,619
I'm not angry. Go ahead.

22
00:01:38,619 --> 00:01:42,519
I'll drink, eat kabobs, and watch the game, anything but coach the track and field team.

23
00:01:42,519 --> 00:01:44,280
What can you do about me?

24
00:01:44,280 --> 00:01:46,980
Sure, don't come begging me after.

25
00:01:46,980 --> 00:01:49,419
I won't beg you.

26
00:01:51,480 --> 00:01:55,300
Boss, I'll take it to go. Deliver it upstairs. Put it on his tab.

27
00:01:55,300 --> 00:01:56,900
Jin Libin!

28
00:01:59,760 --> 00:02:04,139
Boss, Jin loves to eat spicy food lately. Add a butt load of peppers.

29
00:02:04,139 --> 00:02:05,859
Got it.

30
00:02:09,430 --> 00:02:12,179
That'll show you.

31
00:02:13,940 --> 00:02:15,599
Jackpot! Jackpot!

32
00:02:15,599 --> 00:02:17,499
What's with the ruckus?

33
00:02:17,499 --> 00:02:19,300
Let's go check it out.

34
00:02:19,300 --> 00:02:25,839
Jackpot! Jackpot!

35
00:02:25,839 --> 00:02:27,539
Jin Doudou!

36
00:02:32,370 --> 00:02:35,119
Who allowed you to come here by yourself?

37
00:02:35,119 --> 00:02:40,520
Sister, if you didn't scream, I would've won the first prize. I only get lipstick now.

38
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:44,380
What lipstick? I'll tell Mom and Dad when I get home. Dad will smack you!

39
00:02:44,380 --> 00:02:47,579
Sister, you won't do that.

40
00:02:47,579 --> 00:02:52,080
Fine, give me the lipstick and I won't tell them.

41
00:02:54,020 --> 00:02:55,960
Dear Sister Tian Meng,

42
00:02:55,960 --> 00:03:00,399
would you please put in a good word for me in front of Mr. Ma?

43
00:03:00,399 --> 00:03:05,039
You're pretty smart, Doudou. Come on, I'll treat you to something delicious.

44
00:03:06,080 --> 00:03:07,599
That little ass-kisser.

45
00:03:07,599 --> 00:03:11,000
Why... why is Doudou so nice to Meng?

46
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:16,379
Meng's mom is Doudou's class advisor. That's why Doudou is really afraid of Meng.

47
00:03:21,630 --> 00:03:23,439
Watch and learn.

48
00:03:36,810 --> 00:03:39,499
Sir, is there something wrong with your gun?

49
00:03:41,960 --> 00:03:44,460
I don't believe it.

50
00:03:45,870 --> 00:03:48,159
You fired all the bullets.

51
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:54,100
Xiaowen, you try it.

52
00:04:05,380 --> 00:04:08,340
Come on. Out of the way.

53
00:04:08,340 --> 00:04:10,519
Can you do it?

54
00:04:10,519 --> 00:04:12,939
I'll teach you.

55
00:04:12,939 --> 00:04:16,480
First of all, you have to aim. You don't even have the right posture, you know?

56
00:04:16,480 --> 00:04:20,480
Align these three points, your eyes, the telescopic sight, and your target.

57
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:24,739
After that, press the gun stock against your shoulder or it will shake when you fire.

58
00:04:24,739 --> 00:04:26,839
After that,

59
00:04:26,839 --> 00:04:30,060
load it and aim.

60
00:04:30,060 --> 00:04:34,560
Look, do you see that? How's that? Gunslinger of Tieyuan.

61
00:04:34,560 --> 00:04:36,520
Let me try again.

62
00:04:36,520 --> 00:04:39,179
- Go away. Go buy me some ice cream.
- Let me try it.

63
00:04:39,179 --> 00:04:42,620
Go away. Hurry up. Go.

64
00:04:44,870 --> 00:04:46,779
Fine.

65
00:04:48,120 --> 00:04:49,520
Come on.

66
00:05:02,750 --> 00:05:06,399
You've never played this when you were a child?

67
00:05:09,310 --> 00:05:12,280
What did you play, then?

68
00:05:12,280 --> 00:05:13,879
I ran.

69
00:05:15,920 --> 00:05:18,560
About the competition...

70
00:05:28,830 --> 00:05:30,439
Gao Yang,

71
00:05:32,160 --> 00:05:36,819
I am pretty upset about not winning the competition.

72
00:05:38,430 --> 00:05:40,339
But I don't regret it.

73
00:05:41,480 --> 00:05:43,900
I was afraid something might happen to you.

74
00:05:47,560 --> 00:05:50,519
What could happen to me? Don't overthink it.

75
00:05:50,519 --> 00:05:52,980
I can't control myself.

76
00:05:56,820 --> 00:05:59,859
I don't want to lose anyone else again.

77
00:06:05,720 --> 00:06:07,999
You don't have to worry about me.

78
00:06:11,800 --> 00:06:13,300
Okay.

79
00:06:15,430 --> 00:06:19,539
I won't overthink it. You shouldn't feel guilty anymore.

80
00:06:19,539 --> 00:06:20,960
Okay.

81
00:06:22,750 --> 00:06:24,359
Let's compete.

82
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:29,399
Bring it on. I'm not scared of you.

83
00:06:31,110 --> 00:06:36,048
[Episode 15: The Stubborn Kindness]

84
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:53,799
- Hey, Boss.
- You won the first prize, Boy.

85
00:06:53,799 --> 00:06:54,979
Wait, what the hell is this?

86
00:06:54,979 --> 00:06:56,600
A Limited Edition of Haier Brothers.

87
00:06:56,600 --> 00:07:00,360
- Who are you trying to fool? That's the first prize? No, give me something else.
- I don't have anything else.

88
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:02,290
That's not going to work. This is...

89
00:07:02,290 --> 00:07:05,319
I think it's nice. This will do. Thank you, Boss.

90
00:07:05,319 --> 00:07:07,119
Come again next time.

91
00:07:07,119 --> 00:07:08,999
Tourist trap.

92
00:07:10,900 --> 00:07:13,300
What is this?

93
00:07:13,300 --> 00:07:16,459
So, that's what you like? I'll buy you more later.

94
00:07:16,459 --> 00:07:18,560
What is this?

95
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:20,319
Where did you go?

96
00:07:20,319 --> 00:07:23,460
Gao Yang, you're not pulling your donkey face anymore?

97
00:07:23,460 --> 00:07:26,279
I'm a man. I can let bygones be bygones.

98
00:07:26,279 --> 00:07:31,479
That's right. The most important thing is to be happy.

99
00:07:31,479 --> 00:07:33,259
Tieyuan Carnival, let's go!

100
00:07:33,259 --> 00:07:37,200
Let's go! Hurry, hurry.

101
00:08:14,110 --> 00:08:15,680
Go, go, go!

102
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:19,750
Ready!

103
00:08:49,150 --> 00:08:51,379
Xiaowen, what are you looking at?

104
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:57,219
This, it's our graduation picture.

105
00:08:57,219 --> 00:09:01,080
Beijing University of Technology.

106
00:09:01,080 --> 00:09:03,360
Both of us graduated from the Beijing University of Technology.

107
00:09:03,360 --> 00:09:05,320
I want to go to the Beijing University of Technology too.

108
00:09:05,320 --> 00:09:07,940
Well, you have to study hard then.

109
00:09:54,550 --> 00:09:56,559
Are you going to run?

110
00:09:58,670 --> 00:09:59,979
I'm not running today.

111
00:10:01,399 --> 00:10:03,740
Then why did you wake up so early?

112
00:10:12,360 --> 00:10:14,439
- Did you see the contest last night?
- Yes, I did.

113
00:10:14,439 --> 00:10:15,600
Who do you like?

114
00:10:15,600 --> 00:10:17,579
Chun.

115
00:10:18,600 --> 00:10:20,839
Remember to vote for her.

116
00:10:25,639 --> 00:10:28,899
What's going on?

117
00:10:28,899 --> 00:10:31,380
You haven't been training lately.

118
00:10:31,380 --> 00:10:33,380
I want to take a break.

119
00:10:34,559 --> 00:10:36,859
You should take a break.

120
00:10:36,859 --> 00:10:40,279
Let me tell you, you've been training too hard before.

121
00:10:40,279 --> 00:10:43,779
That's not scientific at all. Get some rest.

122
00:10:47,399 --> 00:10:49,299
Beibei,

123
00:10:49,299 --> 00:10:50,600
what do you want for lunch?

124
00:10:50,600 --> 00:10:52,659
I want chicken drumsticks.

125
00:10:54,020 --> 00:10:56,020
It's on him.

126
00:10:58,559 --> 00:11:03,880
Our school achieved an outstanding result during this long-distance race,

127
00:11:03,880 --> 00:11:05,919
especially Sophomore Mi Jia.

128
00:11:05,919 --> 00:11:09,039
She came in first in the women's group. Very good.

129
00:11:09,039 --> 00:11:13,039
It's an honor for our school and the pride of our sports department.

130
00:11:13,039 --> 00:11:14,639
Applaud.

131
00:11:15,879 --> 00:11:19,039
This is a good seedling that Mr. Gao brought to our school.

132
00:11:19,039 --> 00:11:20,639
That's right.

133
00:11:20,639 --> 00:11:24,279
Now, the pre-Olympic track and field team has been established.

134
00:11:24,279 --> 00:11:29,299
Mr. Gao, if you need any help from the younger staff, just tell me.

135
00:11:31,039 --> 00:11:33,919
Vice Principal, I was just about to mention that.

136
00:11:33,919 --> 00:11:36,259
Since all the PE teachers are here,

137
00:11:36,259 --> 00:11:40,559
I think the coach of the track and field team should...

138
00:11:40,559 --> 00:11:42,080
Principal Jin is here.

139
00:11:42,080 --> 00:11:44,440
Hello, Principal Jin.

140
00:11:50,480 --> 00:11:52,360
Well, I'll cut to the chase.

141
00:11:52,360 --> 00:11:57,319
Our school's track and field team needs a new coach.

142
00:11:58,919 --> 00:12:00,440
Who's capable of this task?

143
00:12:00,440 --> 00:12:02,640
Isn't Mr. Gao the coach?

144
00:12:06,200 --> 00:12:10,619
Well, Xiao Li, can you take the job?

145
00:12:10,619 --> 00:12:12,100
I...

146
00:12:13,960 --> 00:12:15,399
Mr. Gao is more experienced than I am.

147
00:12:15,399 --> 00:12:18,039
I think Li is a good candidate.

148
00:12:18,039 --> 00:12:19,799
You can continue with the meeting.

149
00:12:25,159 --> 00:12:27,939
I think Xiao Li is a good candidate, too!

150
00:12:28,759 --> 00:12:30,320
I...

151
00:12:30,320 --> 00:12:33,480
Au-auntie, please... give me some scrambled eggs with tomatoes,

152
00:12:33,480 --> 00:12:35,800
broccoli,

153
00:12:37,480 --> 00:12:39,679
and... and fried chicken fillet.

154
00:12:39,679 --> 00:12:43,519
Jia'er, those boys keep staring at me.

155
00:12:43,519 --> 00:12:44,799
I'm so distressed.

156
00:12:44,799 --> 00:12:47,480
Who's staring at you? They're staring at Mi Jia.

157
00:12:47,480 --> 00:12:51,720
She's famous now after she got first place. You're nobody.

158
00:12:54,879 --> 00:12:57,720
Can... can I have more tomatoes?

159
00:12:57,720 --> 00:13:01,320
What's going on? What are you looking at in broad daylight?

160
00:13:01,320 --> 00:13:03,360
I'm about to lose my cool!

161
00:13:03,360 --> 00:13:05,600
Give me... four steamed buns.

162
00:13:05,600 --> 00:13:06,600
She eats so much.

163
00:13:06,600 --> 00:13:08,020
- Jia'er.
- Thank you.

164
00:13:08,020 --> 00:13:09,600
Be more ladylike.

165
00:13:09,600 --> 00:13:10,720
What did I do?

166
00:13:10,720 --> 00:13:14,620
Learn from me. You see, pretty girls like us are all like this.

167
00:13:14,620 --> 00:13:16,660
We only eat a little bit.

168
00:13:16,660 --> 00:13:18,120
You eat ten meals a day.

169
00:13:18,120 --> 00:13:19,480
Gao Yang!

170
00:13:19,480 --> 00:13:22,480
Thank you, Auntie.

171
00:13:23,159 --> 00:13:24,759
So annoying.

172
00:13:26,320 --> 00:13:30,280
Auntie, I want everything except the two vegetarian dishes.

173
00:13:33,080 --> 00:13:34,440
Eat without me, Gao Yang.

174
00:13:34,440 --> 00:13:35,799
What's wrong?

175
00:13:35,799 --> 00:13:39,339
I... I'm going to look up some information.

176
00:13:40,360 --> 00:13:42,160
You're not eating lunch?

177
00:14:00,399 --> 00:14:02,199
Hello, Miss.

178
00:14:45,590 --> 00:14:48,420
[Free Education for Normal Students]

179
00:14:48,420 --> 00:14:50,240
You want to go to the normal university?

180
00:14:51,450 --> 00:14:52,870
Yes?

181
00:14:55,720 --> 00:14:56,919
I'm just looking.

182
00:14:56,919 --> 00:14:58,999
Who's going to the normal university then?

183
00:15:01,120 --> 00:15:02,820
Who is it?

184
00:15:04,279 --> 00:15:07,380
Architecture? You want to build a house?

185
00:15:09,639 --> 00:15:11,139
What are you doing here?

186
00:15:11,139 --> 00:15:13,519
I'm here to read The Legend of the Condor Heroes.

187
00:15:13,519 --> 00:15:15,799
Huang Yaoshi, Ouyang Feng, Duan Zhixing, and Zhou Botong.

188
00:15:15,799 --> 00:15:19,579
I think Zhou Botong's experiences are similar to mine.

189
00:15:19,579 --> 00:15:22,360
This is a really good book.

190
00:15:22,360 --> 00:15:24,080
Wanyan Honglie...

191
00:15:24,080 --> 00:15:25,980
Well, read it then.

192
00:15:34,799 --> 00:15:37,499
[Recruitment Guidelines for Normal Universities]

193
00:15:50,000 --> 00:15:55,399
Gao Bin, he's pissing me off. He has no respect for rules or discipline.

194
00:15:55,399 --> 00:15:57,859
Do you think I can't do it without you?

195
00:16:01,120 --> 00:16:02,720
Please come in.

196
00:16:02,720 --> 00:16:05,519
Principal Jin, there's a letter from Beijing.

197
00:16:05,519 --> 00:16:08,059
- Thank you.
- You're welcome.

198
00:16:13,600 --> 00:16:16,040
What is it?

199
00:16:16,040 --> 00:16:19,860
[Beijing Olympic Games Committee]

200
00:16:27,639 --> 00:16:30,899
Mi Jia, I'll take care of your duty from now on.

201
00:16:34,279 --> 00:16:35,519
Mi Jia.

202
00:16:35,519 --> 00:16:38,339
Come here. I want to tell you something.

203
00:16:38,339 --> 00:16:40,120
Are the shoes you sold me new?

204
00:16:40,120 --> 00:16:42,600
What are you talking about? My mom bought them for me.

205
00:16:42,600 --> 00:16:43,840
Give them back if you don't want them. Give them to me.

206
00:16:43,840 --> 00:16:45,159
No, I won't.

207
00:16:45,159 --> 00:16:46,919
Then why are you talking nonsense? Let's go, Mi Jia.

208
00:16:46,919 --> 00:16:48,900
- I'll buy you a torch ice-cream.
- Okay.

209
00:16:48,900 --> 00:16:51,740
Mi Jia! I can treat you too!

210
00:16:54,399 --> 00:16:57,920
- Mi Jia. Here you go. Here's your torch.
- Thank you.

211
00:16:57,920 --> 00:16:59,879
Eat it. Eat as much as you want.

212
00:16:59,879 --> 00:17:02,860
Well, there's more if you want.

213
00:17:03,530 --> 00:17:05,879
What do you think? Does it take good?

214
00:17:06,640 --> 00:17:08,540
You want to be a teacher?

215
00:17:09,920 --> 00:17:12,279
Can... can I be a teacher?

216
00:17:12,279 --> 00:17:14,319
Then who wants to be a teacher?

217
00:17:14,319 --> 00:17:16,219
You're asking me?

218
00:17:16,219 --> 00:17:19,140
Then why is Xiaowen looking up information on normal universities?

219
00:17:22,519 --> 00:17:23,680
I... I have to go.

220
00:17:23,680 --> 00:17:26,179
Wait a minute.

221
00:17:27,000 --> 00:17:28,279
Why?

222
00:17:28,279 --> 00:17:30,499
You two have secrets now?

223
00:17:30,499 --> 00:17:32,559
Doesn't Xiaowen want to go to the Beijing University of Technology?

224
00:17:32,559 --> 00:17:34,160
Why did he change his mind?

225
00:17:34,160 --> 00:17:37,780
Xiaowen... Xiaowen doesn't want me to tell you.

226
00:17:38,279 --> 00:17:41,860
But you already ate the torch. Just tell me.

227
00:17:42,920 --> 00:17:45,819
You can have it back. I don't want it anymore.

228
00:17:46,640 --> 00:17:49,019
We all meant well for Xiaowen.

229
00:17:49,019 --> 00:17:50,979
Just say it.

230
00:17:53,359 --> 00:17:55,380
Just tell me.

231
00:17:57,640 --> 00:18:01,780
Xiaowen didn't make it to the nationals,

232
00:18:01,780 --> 00:18:07,580
so he can't get the scholarship. That's why he wants to go to a free university.

233
00:18:07,580 --> 00:18:08,799
But...

234
00:18:08,799 --> 00:18:10,720
Gao Bin will pay for his tuition.

235
00:18:10,720 --> 00:18:13,000
He doesn't want to spend Mr. Gao's money.

236
00:18:13,000 --> 00:18:15,020
Well, does Xiaowen want to go to the Beijing University of Technology anyway?

237
00:18:15,020 --> 00:18:16,820
He does.

238
00:18:17,680 --> 00:18:23,019
The Beijing University of Technology was the Alma Mater of Xiaowen's parents.

239
00:18:24,019 --> 00:18:29,140
Xiaowen's parents both graduated from the Beijing University of Technology?

240
00:18:36,279 --> 00:18:37,979
Just eat it.

241
00:19:20,200 --> 00:19:21,359
My tea isn't good enough.

242
00:19:21,359 --> 00:19:24,320
If you want to drink tea, go back to your own office.

243
00:19:24,320 --> 00:19:26,819
This is just an equipment room.

244
00:19:26,819 --> 00:19:29,900
From now on, you can't use this as an office, understand?

245
00:19:31,359 --> 00:19:33,920
Why? Are you going to fire me?

246
00:19:33,920 --> 00:19:37,000
Judging by your current behavior, you're asking to be fired.

247
00:19:37,000 --> 00:19:40,739
Let me tell you, Jin Libin, don't you threaten me!

248
00:19:40,739 --> 00:19:44,459
I mean it when I said I can afford to raise Xiaowen. This is a man's pride, you know?

249
00:19:44,459 --> 00:19:46,440
No, that's not what I want to say.

250
00:19:46,440 --> 00:19:49,720
I know what you want to say. You think Li is better than me, right?

251
00:19:49,720 --> 00:19:53,600
Go to him then! I don't want to be the coach anymore!

252
00:19:58,519 --> 00:20:01,240
Are you an idiot? Oh, my God!

253
00:20:08,640 --> 00:20:10,340
Come on.

254
00:20:12,480 --> 00:20:14,480
Yang, enjoy it.

255
00:20:14,480 --> 00:20:16,680
Put it on Bin's tab.

256
00:20:18,640 --> 00:20:20,640
There's food at home. Why are we eating out?

257
00:20:20,640 --> 00:20:23,160
Sometimes men need some leisure time.

258
00:20:23,160 --> 00:20:24,759
I don't need that.

259
00:20:24,759 --> 00:20:26,519
Yes, you do. Cheers.

260
00:20:26,519 --> 00:20:28,620
Why exactly did you bring me out?

261
00:20:28,620 --> 00:20:35,139
Well, let's eat first. I'll tell you after. Come on, try this.

262
00:20:38,599 --> 00:20:40,900
What do you think? Is it delicious?

263
00:20:41,559 --> 00:20:43,059
It's alright.

264
00:20:44,160 --> 00:20:48,400
I'm telling you, if the kabobs are delicious, we'll come out for some kabobs

265
00:20:48,400 --> 00:20:50,160
instead of eating that nasty meal at home.

266
00:20:50,160 --> 00:20:52,439
We only live once.

267
00:20:52,439 --> 00:20:57,019
We should live a splendid and joyful life. Come on, let's drink.

268
00:20:57,019 --> 00:20:59,800
That's you, not me.

269
00:21:04,319 --> 00:21:06,019
Xiaowen,

270
00:21:08,960 --> 00:21:12,640
what were you looking up in the library today?

271
00:21:13,759 --> 00:21:15,659
What does that have to do with you?

272
00:21:16,519 --> 00:21:19,360
I have to put some sense in you.

273
00:21:19,360 --> 00:21:20,640
It's not impossible for you.

274
00:21:20,640 --> 00:21:25,460
You have such good grades. You shouldn't give up your previous aspiration.

275
00:21:28,599 --> 00:21:29,920
Did Mi Jia tell you?

276
00:21:29,920 --> 00:21:32,219
It doesn't matter who told me.

277
00:21:32,219 --> 00:21:35,559
Xiaowen, you should go to the Beijing University of Technology.

278
00:21:36,200 --> 00:21:38,300
I'm not going there.

279
00:21:38,300 --> 00:21:41,799
Why not? Isn't that your parents' Alma Mater?

280
00:21:43,400 --> 00:21:45,400
What does that have to do with you?

281
00:21:46,079 --> 00:21:47,779
Wait, Xiaowen.

282
00:21:47,779 --> 00:21:49,200
Xiaowen.

283
00:21:49,200 --> 00:21:52,340
Xiaowen, stop right there. Let's set the record straight, Xiaowen.

284
00:21:52,340 --> 00:21:53,880
I told you it's none of your business!

285
00:21:53,880 --> 00:21:56,599
Stop worrying about the tuition. Let Gao Bin pay for it.

286
00:21:56,599 --> 00:21:58,780
I don't want to spend Mr. Gao's money. Do you understand?

287
00:21:58,780 --> 00:22:01,599
He brought you here. That's his responsibility. He should pay for it.

288
00:22:01,599 --> 00:22:03,039
He has no obligation to do that!

289
00:22:03,039 --> 00:22:05,440
I already appreciate him for putting me through high school.

290
00:22:05,440 --> 00:22:08,539
What about college? What are you going to do for college?

291
00:22:13,240 --> 00:22:15,500
It's already good enough

292
00:22:16,559 --> 00:22:20,999
for kids from the orphanage like us to go to college.

293
00:22:21,519 --> 00:22:24,119
I really don't mind whether it's the Beijing University of Technology or not.

294
00:22:24,119 --> 00:22:26,040
Why are you so stubborn?

295
00:22:26,040 --> 00:22:28,914
I can't be accepted to the Beijing University of Technology even if I want to go there.

296
00:22:31,240 --> 00:22:33,880
Gao Yang, I can't get through to you.

297
00:22:34,640 --> 00:22:38,100
- Is it because Gao Bin is poor?
- It has nothing to do with him!

298
00:22:39,440 --> 00:22:42,279
I don't want to trouble him anymore.

299
00:22:42,279 --> 00:22:45,559
That's enough. I'll go ask Gao Bin.

300
00:22:50,440 --> 00:22:51,759
Gao Bin!

301
00:22:51,759 --> 00:22:53,039
What's wrong?

302
00:22:53,039 --> 00:22:55,400
What did you tell Xiaowen when you took him home?

303
00:22:55,400 --> 00:22:57,599
Did you say you'll only support him through high school?

304
00:22:57,599 --> 00:23:00,960
No. I told him I would put him through college.

305
00:23:00,960 --> 00:23:03,060
Well, where's the money for his tuition?

306
00:23:03,839 --> 00:23:06,279
Why should you care about that?

307
00:23:06,279 --> 00:23:10,500
Xiaowen is not going to the Beijing University of Technology because you're poor! Did you know that?

308
00:23:10,500 --> 00:23:12,759
Do you have money or not?

309
00:23:16,240 --> 00:23:18,900
I don't have money now.

310
00:23:18,900 --> 00:23:23,419
But I still have two more years. I'll surely have the money in two years.

311
00:23:23,419 --> 00:23:26,400
- Show me your passbook.
- Why do you want to see that?

312
00:23:27,519 --> 00:23:28,720
Just show me!

313
00:23:28,720 --> 00:23:33,039
Why do you want to see it? I told you I'll have money!

314
00:23:33,039 --> 00:23:35,539
- Let me see it!
- No!

315
00:23:36,780 --> 00:23:38,580
Let me see it!

316
00:23:39,279 --> 00:23:41,700
We don't have money!

317
00:23:41,700 --> 00:23:43,659
We're broke!

318
00:23:45,279 --> 00:23:47,500
Are you happy now?

319
00:24:00,599 --> 00:24:03,019
Don't we need to spend money on living expenses?

320
00:24:04,200 --> 00:24:07,680
Which child in Tieyuan has more allowances than you?

321
00:24:08,640 --> 00:24:12,439
You don't need to worry about Xiaowen's tuition. I have my ways! I can pay for yours as well!

322
00:24:12,439 --> 00:24:16,319
You two should just focus on school. Don't worry about the rest.

323
00:24:19,559 --> 00:24:21,559
What ways?

324
00:24:21,559 --> 00:24:23,780
Can you name it?

325
00:24:28,480 --> 00:24:31,140
- What are you doing?
- Calling my mom.

326
00:24:33,720 --> 00:24:35,000
What are you doing?

327
00:24:35,000 --> 00:24:38,440
Gao Yang, just trust me once.

328
00:24:38,440 --> 00:24:40,240
I have my ways.

329
00:24:41,440 --> 00:24:43,540
I don't believe you!

330
00:24:43,540 --> 00:24:45,559
I'll sell the house!

331
00:24:49,480 --> 00:24:52,140
- What did you say?
- I said I'll sell the house.

332
00:24:52,140 --> 00:24:54,119
I already figured it out before Xiaowen arrived.

333
00:24:54,119 --> 00:24:57,359
I'll sell this house to put you two through college.

334
00:24:57,359 --> 00:24:59,419
Then, I'll buy a smaller one.

335
00:25:00,119 --> 00:25:01,619
Anyway...

336
00:25:05,880 --> 00:25:08,080
You're not coming back anyway.

337
00:25:10,200 --> 00:25:12,000
You can't sell it!

338
00:25:21,319 --> 00:25:24,359
You... How are you winding it?

339
00:25:24,359 --> 00:25:26,880
Did the yarn offend you?

340
00:25:26,880 --> 00:25:29,040
The yarn didn't offend me.

341
00:25:29,659 --> 00:25:31,780
I... Gao Bin offended me.

342
00:25:31,780 --> 00:25:35,219
That's enough. You've been friends with Bin for so many years. That's not necessary.

343
00:25:35,219 --> 00:25:38,099
What do you mean not necessary?

344
00:25:38,099 --> 00:25:41,300
I asked him to be the coach so he can earn more money.

345
00:25:41,300 --> 00:25:45,599
Was that wrong? What did I get? He wants to quit.

346
00:25:45,599 --> 00:25:47,160
Does he think he's Hanxin?

347
00:25:47,160 --> 00:25:49,000
He wants me to run after him under the moonlight?

348
00:25:49,000 --> 00:25:52,720
He's a man. You said he's poor. If I were him, I would be mad at you too.

349
00:25:52,720 --> 00:25:55,600
I'm just telling the truth. He is poor.

350
00:25:55,600 --> 00:26:01,020
When we first came into the No. 3 High School together, he was such a big spender.

351
00:26:01,020 --> 00:26:03,160
His parents work for a state-owned enterprise. His family was well off.

352
00:26:03,160 --> 00:26:06,039
Then what happened? They didn't save a dime.

353
00:26:06,039 --> 00:26:09,680
Now, his parents passed away. Who's going to support him?

354
00:26:09,680 --> 00:26:12,160
You don't say. You do make some sense.

355
00:26:12,160 --> 00:26:15,319
The two kids are going to college now. He'll definitely need to spend more money.

356
00:26:15,319 --> 00:26:18,359
Exactly. Why didn't he think about that?

357
00:26:18,359 --> 00:26:21,140
What is that? Good news from Beijing?

358
00:26:21,140 --> 00:26:24,240
Why didn't you give it to him and convince him nicely?

359
00:26:24,240 --> 00:26:25,480
I'm not going.

360
00:26:25,480 --> 00:26:31,280
Him? He's an insolent, arrogant, ungrateful, improper fellow!

361
00:26:32,359 --> 00:26:34,200
Judging from your attitude...

362
00:26:34,200 --> 00:26:36,759
What's going on? Are you not planning to let him coach the track and field anymore?

363
00:26:36,759 --> 00:26:40,880
Why should he coach the team? There're so many young talents in the school.

364
00:26:40,880 --> 00:26:43,079
He's not even close.

365
00:26:45,350 --> 00:26:49,079
Why should I wind this? I don't know how. I'm not doing it anymore.

366
00:26:49,079 --> 00:26:51,399
What did the yarn do to you?

367
00:26:51,399 --> 00:26:52,720
Tutor him nicely.

368
00:26:52,720 --> 00:26:54,079
Write it nicely.

369
00:26:54,079 --> 00:26:56,580
What the hell is this?

370
00:27:00,039 --> 00:27:01,839
Beibei,

371
00:27:01,839 --> 00:27:04,380
- give this to Uncle Bin.
- I haven't finished my homework yet, Mom.

372
00:27:04,380 --> 00:27:06,039
So naughty.

373
00:27:06,039 --> 00:27:09,079
Doudou, be a good boy. Come here.

374
00:27:09,680 --> 00:27:12,260
Be a good boy and bring this to Uncle Bin.

375
00:27:12,260 --> 00:27:13,880
I want ice-cream.

376
00:27:13,880 --> 00:27:17,180
Uncle Bin has ice-cream at his place. Go on.

377
00:27:21,279 --> 00:27:22,880
Don't say anything, you two.

378
00:27:22,880 --> 00:27:24,440
I will sell this house and that's final.

379
00:27:24,440 --> 00:27:27,359
Look at the state of it.

380
00:27:27,359 --> 00:27:29,699
It's got bad plumbing. The toilet clogs all the time.

381
00:27:29,699 --> 00:27:32,720
It's not facing a good direction either. I'll definitely sell it for a new one.

382
00:27:32,720 --> 00:27:34,839
I can even hear your snores.

383
00:27:34,839 --> 00:27:39,099
Sell the house if you want. It has nothing to do with me.

384
00:27:39,099 --> 00:27:41,279
I've already decided to go to a normal university.

385
00:27:41,279 --> 00:27:43,519
No, Xiaowen. Just let him sell it.

386
00:27:43,519 --> 00:27:47,960
You have no idea how much money Gao Bin took from my grandparents all his life.

387
00:27:47,960 --> 00:27:49,920
He should be an adult now.

388
00:27:49,920 --> 00:27:53,160
No, Gao Yang. What does it have to do with you?

389
00:27:53,160 --> 00:27:56,160
I'm talking to Xiaowen. Go back to your room.

390
00:27:56,160 --> 00:27:58,200
If you're reliable, would you need to sell the house?

391
00:27:58,200 --> 00:28:00,000
Xiaowen doesn't want to use your money because you're poor.

392
00:28:00,000 --> 00:28:01,699
- I never said that.
- Then go to the Beijing University of Technology.

393
00:28:01,699 --> 00:28:05,540
- I'm not going.
- Shut up, all of you. There's an adult in the house.

394
00:28:05,540 --> 00:28:06,759
I'm not going anyway.

395
00:28:06,759 --> 00:28:08,880
Xiaowen, say no more. I'm selling this house for sure.

396
00:28:08,880 --> 00:28:12,000
Fine, go ahead and sell it.

397
00:28:13,079 --> 00:28:14,680
I'll go back to the orphanage.

398
00:28:14,680 --> 00:28:17,779
- Don't!
- Don't! No, Xiaowen! No! I... Well... well...

399
00:28:17,779 --> 00:28:20,359
I won't go to college. You go!

400
00:28:21,079 --> 00:28:23,039
Why are you just like your dad?

401
00:28:23,039 --> 00:28:25,759
Wait. What did I do?

402
00:28:25,759 --> 00:28:27,119
Mr. Gao, I didn't mean that.

403
00:28:27,119 --> 00:28:28,640
How am I like him?

404
00:28:28,640 --> 00:28:30,599
What's wrong with being like me? I'm your dad!

405
00:28:30,599 --> 00:28:33,719
- You're unreliable!
- How did you grow up if I'm unreliable?

406
00:28:33,719 --> 00:28:35,739
You can't leave!

407
00:28:38,480 --> 00:28:40,180
Mr. Gao!

408
00:28:40,180 --> 00:28:42,380
Someone's at the door.

409
00:28:42,880 --> 00:28:43,920
Go on.

410
00:28:43,920 --> 00:28:45,520
Hold onto him.

411
00:28:47,499 --> 00:28:51,260
"As the whole nation enhances the physical strength of our youth to welcome the Beijing Olympic Games,

412
00:28:51,260 --> 00:28:56,359
We will increase the quota for participants for the current National High School Games."

413
00:28:56,359 --> 00:28:59,359
Xiaowen, they increased the quota of participants! You still have a chance!

414
00:29:02,559 --> 00:29:05,319
The national policy is awesome!

415
00:29:05,319 --> 00:29:09,640
Wait, they told me this time will be different when I went to Beijing for the conference.

416
00:29:09,640 --> 00:29:12,780
- Why did I forget?
- That's nonsense. Because you're unreliable.

417
00:29:13,400 --> 00:29:18,280
From now on, I will surely be reliable. I will prove myself.

418
00:29:18,280 --> 00:29:21,659
Xiaowen, we have to

419
00:29:21,659 --> 00:29:23,560
win this preliminary competition.

420
00:29:23,560 --> 00:29:25,459
I will do my best.

421
00:29:26,759 --> 00:29:29,019
Doudou had too much ice cream.

422
00:29:33,799 --> 00:29:36,900
I just quit my coach position for the track and field team.

423
00:29:36,900 --> 00:29:39,039
What's wrong with you, Gao Bin?

424
00:29:39,039 --> 00:29:41,959
Don't panic. I'll go remedy the situation now.

425
00:29:45,359 --> 00:29:48,759
Doudou, is your dad home?

426
00:29:49,279 --> 00:29:51,319
Is he angry?

427
00:29:51,319 --> 00:29:54,540
My dad is furious!

428
00:29:58,759 --> 00:30:02,359
Let's go.

429
00:30:02,359 --> 00:30:05,519
Doudou said his dad is angry! Let's do it another day!

430
00:30:05,519 --> 00:30:08,319
No, you've waited all night!

431
00:30:10,119 --> 00:30:14,400
Tomorrow. Tomorrow, I'll talk to Jin in his office.

432
00:30:14,400 --> 00:30:16,959
Xiaowen, what do you think?

433
00:30:17,519 --> 00:30:20,119
Mr. Gao, good luck.

434
00:30:20,119 --> 00:30:22,199
Good luck, go knock on the door.

435
00:30:36,230 --> 00:30:37,840
No one's home.

436
00:30:39,400 --> 00:30:42,300
Principal Jin!

437
00:30:42,300 --> 00:30:43,720
I told you no one's home.

438
00:30:43,720 --> 00:30:45,520
What are you doing?

439
00:30:45,520 --> 00:30:46,960
You're here.

440
00:30:46,960 --> 00:30:48,519
Nothing.

441
00:30:48,519 --> 00:30:50,160
Why are you knocking if it's nothing?

442
00:30:50,160 --> 00:30:52,420
I... I just passed by.

443
00:30:52,420 --> 00:30:54,900
Principal Jin, he's here to apologize.

444
00:30:54,900 --> 00:30:59,620
- Thank you, Mrs. Jin.
- You're welcome. Bin, start eating.

445
00:30:59,620 --> 00:31:01,319
Where are the boys?

446
00:31:01,319 --> 00:31:04,519
They're busy with something. I told them to go home first.

447
00:31:10,340 --> 00:31:14,580
Well... I'll go make another dish for you.

448
00:31:26,480 --> 00:31:28,080
I'm sorry.

449
00:31:34,480 --> 00:31:38,799
I am sorry.

450
00:31:44,720 --> 00:31:47,499
I said I'm sorry. Did you hear me?

451
00:31:47,499 --> 00:31:49,180
I want to be the coach.

452
00:31:52,960 --> 00:31:55,080
- Did I force you to do it?
- No.

453
00:31:55,080 --> 00:31:59,839
I want to coach the track and field team eagerly, profoundly, and earnestly.

454
00:31:59,839 --> 00:32:01,079
No.

455
00:32:01,079 --> 00:32:03,640
Just get over it. Don't be difficult.

456
00:32:03,640 --> 00:32:07,499
Why can't I be difficult with you? If I don't do that, would you learn to be responsible?

457
00:32:07,499 --> 00:32:10,839
Do you know how to be a teacher? Do you know how to be a parent?

458
00:32:10,839 --> 00:32:13,340
- Do you know...
- Alright, alright.

459
00:32:13,340 --> 00:32:15,580
If it wasn't for Xiaowen,

460
00:32:16,200 --> 00:32:17,879
I wouldn't come.

461
00:32:17,879 --> 00:32:20,580
That's not just Xiaowen. It's a team.

462
00:32:20,580 --> 00:32:22,480
It's a team, you know?

463
00:32:22,480 --> 00:32:24,839
Alright, I'll surely coach them diligently.

464
00:32:24,839 --> 00:32:26,100
- What about the interview?
- I'll cooperate.

465
00:32:26,100 --> 00:32:29,320
- What about Reporter Niu?
- I'll kiss up to him.

466
00:32:29,320 --> 00:32:31,960
That's more like it. Be more self-aware, okay?

467
00:32:31,960 --> 00:32:35,079
I don't trust anyone with the team. I only trust you, you know?

468
00:32:35,079 --> 00:32:38,380
No problem. Don't worry.

469
00:32:40,440 --> 00:32:43,640
Come on, let's drink to the track and field team of No. 3 High School.

470
00:32:43,640 --> 00:32:46,500
And to your Reporter Niu.

471
00:33:14,070 --> 00:33:20,140
♫  I know the direction of dawn  ♫

472
00:33:20,140 --> 00:33:27,505
♫  It's right in front of me, waiting for me to shine  ♫

473
00:33:27,505 --> 00:33:33,495
♫  The starlight that shines alone the way  ♫

474
00:33:33,495 --> 00:33:39,635
♫  Accompanying me on my adventure, packing my dreams in my heart  ♫

475
00:33:39,635 --> 00:33:46,187
♫  I don't fear the rough journey ahead, I will no longer run away  ♫

476
00:33:46,187 --> 00:33:51,827
♫  Maybe I'm not destined for the hardship of this journey  ♫

477
00:33:51,827 --> 00:33:55,740
♫  To chase after the longing in my heart  ♫

478
00:33:55,740 --> 00:33:59,162
♫  Let's set sail on your dreams  ♫

479
00:33:59,162 --> 00:34:02,457
♫  Let's not have any regrets in our youth  ♫

480
00:34:02,457 --> 00:34:09,217
♫  Even if you stumble and fall, I'll be by your side  ♫

481
00:34:09,217 --> 00:34:12,428
♫  Let's find the answer through the madness  ♫

482
00:34:12,428 --> 00:34:16,640
♫  Let's have courage to ride the waves and billows  ♫

483
00:34:16,640 --> 00:34:20,460
♫  With my wings, I'll fly us to the future  ♫

484
00:34:20,460 --> 00:34:28,420
♫  And step forward into the future without fear of sorrow  ♫
